Do you want your secrets to pop up in your browser history? Neither do we. That's why we created HushFind.

HushFind will make sure to switch to incognito mode whenever you search for something private or visit a sensitive site. 

*** Automatically switch to incognito mode ***

Using built-in intelligence, HushFind detects all sensitive sites you visit and completely clears them from your history. No trace left. Never deal with tedious browser settings again- Hushfind does it for you while you browse.
